
<purchabr>GRANDVIEW</purchabr> ACQUIRES CONTROL OF U.K. TICKET GROUP
    TORONTO, March 9 - <purchaser>Consolidated Grandview Inc</purchaser> said it
acquired a 60 pct stake in {<acquired>All Ticket Group PLC</acquired>}, of <acqloc>London</acqloc>,
for <dlramt>undisclosed</dlramt> terms. The seller was also undisclosed.
    <acqabr>All Ticket</acqabr> is a <acqbus>special events travel company</acqbus> with
exclusive European rights to UAL Inc {UAL}'s United Airlines
Apollo system, booking all United Airlines flights in Britain
and Europe. <acqabr>All Ticket</acqabr> and its subsidiaries will also
co-sponsor various events this year including the British Open
golf tournament and rowing's Henley Regatta.
    Its 1986 revenues totaled 12 mln Canadian dlrs.
   
